text: Ivo Arčanin (16 October 1906 - 27 April 1995) was a Yugoslav swimmer. He competed in the men's 4 × 200 metre freestyle relay event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1906 births Category:1995 deaths Category:Yugoslav male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Yugoslavia Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
